name: Ten Seconds a New Earth
description:
As the countdown sounds every ten seconds, more kinds of food garbage will fall into the sea from the air.
 
Use WASD to control movement / Press space to continue
How many points can this boat collect before garbage fills the whole ocean!
Come and have a try! 

However, no matter what the highest score is, the end of this game must be that one day garbage will fill the whole ocean, even the whole earth..... 
 :(
